International Convention for the Conservation of Atlantic Tunas
PrecisReappointment of SAMUEL GILBERT ELSWORTH of Bridgewater, Nova Scotia, and BARRY DEAN of Cape Tormentine, New Brunswick, as Canadian Commissioners to the International Commission for the Conservation of Atlantic Tunas, to hold office during pleasure for a term ending March 31, 2005.
